SENATE RESOLUTION NO. 39
BY SENATOR BOUDREAUX
COMMENDATIONS. Commends and congratulates Delores Murray on being inducted into
the USATF National Officials Hall of Fame.
1 A RESOLUTION
2 To commend and congratulate Delores Murray on being inducted into the USA Track and
3 Field National Officials Hall of Fame.
4 WHEREAS, the USA Track and Field (USATF) National Officials Hall of Fame
5 honors individuals who exemplify the highest standards of officiating excellence, integrity,
6 and dedication to the sport of track and field; and
7 WHEREAS, inductees into this prestigious hall of fame have demonstrated
8 exceptional commitment to ensuring fairness, equity, and professionalism in athletic
9 competition, while also serving as role models and mentors to future generations of officials;
10 and
11 WHEREAS, on December 4, 2020, Delores Murray was inducted into the USA
12 Track and Field National Officials Hall of Fame in recognition of her exemplary service and
13 distinguished career in track and field officiating; and
14 WHEREAS, Delores Murray has consistently demonstrated superior skill, leadership,
15 and professionalism as a track and field official, earning the respect and deep admiration of
16 her peers, who consider her "a gift to our sport"; and
17 WHEREAS, her expertise has been recognized on the state, national, and
18 international stage, as evidenced by her distinguished record of officiating at multiple United
